title: togrp.com is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA
statement: The ONE Group's website togrp.com is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA accessibility standards.

citations.quote: The One Group (togrp.com) is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Partially conformant means that some parts of the content do not fully conform to the accessibility standard.
